title: BRIEF-Dorota Krawczyk acquires 30.53 pct sake in Igoria Trade
text:
BRIEF-Dorota Krawczyk acquires 30.53 pct sake in Igoria Trade Sept 1 
Sept 1 Igoria Trade SA : 
* Said on Monday Dorota Krawczyk acquired 30.53 percent stake (4,920,000 shares) in the company, on Aug. 26
